INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5007','‘Gold Edition’ contains flakes of real gold, in the shape of Ume flower petals which according to ancient Chinese medicine, helps keep your body in perfect balance.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','8','Remy Martin X.O.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5008','A sumptuous blend of opulent aromas and velvet textures. The unmistakable signature of fine Champagne Cognac, characterized by flavors of lush, ripe fruits that linger generously on th palette.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','9','The Balvenie 17yrs Old' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5009','This is a limited edition single malt whisky that has been 100% handcrafted to express their devotion and craftsmanship. Its excellence is being recognized, as it won several gold medals at the International Spirit Challenge.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','10','Ballantine''s 17 Years' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5010','Ballantine''s 17 Years Old displays all the flavours of Scotland. Its refined sweet oak nose and luscious body makes 17 Years Old one of the world''s most highly acclaimed whiskies.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','11','Ballantine''s 21 Years' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5011','The connoisseur''s blend of whisky, Ballantine''s 21 Years Old has supreme credentials. Its sparkling gold colour, floral nose and aromatic pallet give Ballantine''s 21 Years Old a delightful complexity, making this whisky to savour.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','12','Ballantine''s 30 Years' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5012','Ballantine''s 30 Years Old ranks as one of the world''s most exquisite and expensive blends with a deep quality gold colour, subtle sweet flavour on the nose and a complex pallet of honey and vanilla.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','13','Royal Salute 21 Years' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5013','It carries its years with dignity : a flavor and richness only long aging can give. It appropriately reflects ''The Ultimate Tribute'' worthy to be offered to the Queen.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','14','Limoncino Bottega' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5014','Limoncino Bottega, the traditional Italian lemon liqueur, is made by infusing the peels of Sicilian lemons in alcohol. The addition of the best Veneto grappa makes it sweet and fragrant.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','15','Highland Park 1990' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5015','It is the balance between the smokey spicy notes and fruity sherry sweetness. The mouth watering citrus sensation keeps the flavor developing and eventually a vanilla note wrapped in subtle spice brings the flavor to a long finish.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','16','Camus X.O. Elegance' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5016','It reveals a unique bouquet of floral aromas, tinged with dried fruit, liquorice and spicy notes, with a persistent leathery finish.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','17','Inniskillin Sparkling' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5017','On the palate this Sparkling Icewine shows a very delicate but lively sparkle which is balanced beautifully by its generous natural acidity.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','18','Chabot X.O.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5018','It contains a nose of almond and plum. Presented in a heart-shaped decanter highly decorated in silver.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','19','Choya Umeshu Private' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5019','A masterpiece of CHOYA, which dedicates its time to studying Ume and Umeshu making. Every step of the production was carefully supervised by our Umeshu-makers. Please enjoy this high-quality Umeshu made with large Ume-fruits.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','20','Johnnie Walker Blue' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5020','Created from the rarest and most expensive whiskies in the world, each bottle of Johnnie Walker Blue Label is individually numbered, reflecting its rarity.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','21','Hidden Secret 2007' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5021','The wine shows a deep red color and the nose is invitingly spicy and savory with leathery complexity, complemented by sweet and sour cherries, mulberries and a hint of marzipan.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','22','Landy X.O. No 1' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5022','Coming from the best cognac areas, distilled carefully without any chemical, Landy X.O is internationally recognized and awarded by 21 medals. Average age : 35 years' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','23','Camus Ile De Re' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5023','This cognac owes its character to a unique aging technique. After a first aging in the cellars on the Ile de Ré Island, it undergoes a second maturation in old ''red'' barrels, which have undergone a special toasting process at the cooperage, developed by our Cellar Master.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','24','Glenfiddich 18 Years' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5024','Creating an exceptionally smooth single malt Scotch whisky with notes of spiced apple and robust oak. Each batch is of a unique and of exceptional quality.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','25','Chivas Regal 18 Years' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5025','A super-premium edition of the style made famous by Chivas Regal family, with the richness and depth of 18 years old scotch whiskies. A special and rare blend created by Master Blender Colin Scott.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','26','Highland Park 1994' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5026','The Highland Park 1994 vintage is a lingering, warming smokey whisky. With its warm caramel notes to the fore coupled with hints of almonds, the 1994 is beautifully mature.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','27','Royal Salute 38 Years' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5027','It is a magnificent blended Scotch Whisky poured into exclusive granite effect porcelain flagons.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','28','Inniskillin Ice Wine' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5028','Intense tropical fruit aromas with mango and apricot flavors on the palate. The magic of Inniskillin Icewine is not in its sweetness, but rather the lively acidity that balances this special and rare gift of nature.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','29','Inniskillin Cabernet' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5029','Red Icewine is very rare and difficult to produce. Beautiful ruby red in color with red berry flavors, such as cherry and strawberry. With balanced acidity, this is an amazing pairing with dark chocolate.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','30','Pinnacle Sparkling' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5030','Only the finest hand-picked apples from orchards near the summit of Pinnacle Mountain are used to make Sparkling Summit Selection Ice Apple Wine which can be enjoyed equally well as a before dinner drink, a dessert wine, or with a variety of foods.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','31','Alexander Grappa Rose' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5031','Alexander Grappa is the best Italian distillate obtained from the Italian grape skins. The hand made Murano glass bottle contains a colorful Red Rose, blown by glass master in Venice.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','32','Omearaq Pug Set' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5032','As a result of Globalizational effort of Baesangmyun Brewery, O-mea-raq, was brewed with two main ingredients : Eau-de-vie and roasted plum at 40% Alc.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','33','Chabot 30 Years Old' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5033','The first brandy with a 30 year old age statement. Ever drop of Armagnac in this decanter is 30 years old or older. The innovative, modern and elegant gift packaging makes it an ideal gift.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','34','Landy Mayflower' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5034','Great craftsmanship is dedicated to produce each bottle 100% handmade with unique inside-sculpture. Only a few bottles are released every year.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','35','Level Vodka- Absolut' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5035','Level is made through a combination of two distillation processes, resulting in the perfect balance smoothness and character. Level is produced in Ahus using the same winter wheat and aquified water as the other Absolut products.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','36','Camus Heritage 1975' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5036','This rare, limited edition 1975 Vintage Cognac comes from a magnificent unblended batch distilled by a single grower. The entire stock, after long ageing, yielded only 6,924 bottles are individually numbered and signed.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','37','Royal Salute 100 Cask' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5037','With a special blend of only one hundred rare casks hand-selected by Master Blender, Royal Salute 100 Cask is a new variation of refinement.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','38','La Spinetta 2007' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5038','La Spinetta’s oldest Barbera vines(65yrs) yielding a mere bottle per plant. A full-throttle wine in the classic Asti-style, with a tight, lively core of acidity & spice and explosive fruit.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','39','Johnnie Walker KGV' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5039','Rare oak casks have been used to age precious whiskies crafted in distilleries in existence during the reign of King George V resulting in a highly distinctive whisky, smooth with age and regal in its maturity.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','40','Chabot 1951 Vintage' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5040','It represents 60 years of nature under intense care. Only very limited quantities are available to a privileged few. It is the perfect gift or reward for oneself for a 60th birthday celebration, anniversary, or any other important event.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','41','Macallan 17 Years Old' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5041','It is a result of a unique combination of both bourbon and sherry oak casks. The result is soft and rich Macallan with hints of citrus, tropical fruits, spice and wood smoke, delivering a lingering finish with hints of orange zest.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','42','L''ostal Cazes 2007' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5042','Languedoc is actually the most promising French wine growing area. Following to the success of Chateau Lynch-Bages, the Cazes family created L’ostal Cazes, an estate in the village of La Liviniere.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','43','Domaine Des Senechaux' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5043','Recently bought by Jean-Michel Cazes, owner of the Chateau Lynch-Bages, Domaine des Senechaux is one of the oldest domaines of this area with a history tracing back to the 14th century.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','44','The Macallan Estate' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5044','The Macallan Estate Reserve is a new product of the Macallan family, produced with traditional way of uncooled filtering and bottling. For a deep and rich taste, only small sized sherry cask concentrate has been used in the making.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','45','L’Andrea  2004' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5045','L’Andrea is the result of a selection of the best grapes of our estate. It is a very elegant wine that overwhelms with intense scents of red fruits, tobacco and light hints of sweet marzipan.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','46','Amarone 2007' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5046','Among famous Italian wines, Amarone has the most outstanding personality. Produced in Veneto region since the 4th century, with its intense dry and tannic finishing, it is the best compliment to heavy sourced dish, red meats, roasts and cheeses.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','47','Martell Cordon Bleu' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5047','It''s a unique product within the Martell style of cognac. A true classic, appreciated worldwide.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','48','Shui Jing Fang' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5048','Originating from the end of the Yuan dynasty, continuing through the Ming and Qing dynasties, Shui Jing Fang encompasses 600 years of unique character. (Alcohol : 52%)' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','49','Beaune 1er Cru 2002' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5049','Beaune 1er Cru ''Couchereaux'' has a deep ruby colour. Thanks to its exposure, it develops powerful aromas of matured red fruits. It is a structured wine, with good tannins, rich and able to age.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','50','Hennessy X.O.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5050','The first and genuine ''Extra Old'' cognac. Powerful, masculine and generous. Finally, symbol of luxury !' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','51','Tapanappa 2006' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5051','The Cazes family, renowned for their wine in Bordeaux, worked together with the Bollinger family, known for their Champaign, in creating a world-class wine with a French touch in Australia.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','52','Torres Grans 2002' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5052','Rich aromas of blueberry jam and quince on a background of vanilla and incense. Silky palate showing excellent evolution, elegant and fleshy, with the presence of typical jammy notes together with of fine spices.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','53','Chabot Extra' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5053','This specially blended Armagnac is extremely mellow and rounded, full of body and intense aromas from a long aging process. Combined with an award winning and unique decanter created by French artist Richard Laurent, it is indeed the perfect choice for connoisseurs.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','54','Chateau Brane2003' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5054','A second growth form the magic margaux appellation in the heart of Bordeaux region, Chateau Brane Cantenac belongs to Henri Lurton. The 2003 vintage was probably the hottest and driest vintage for centuries and the wine has a complex toasty nose with hints of vanilla and notes of blackberries.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','55','Greg Norman Limited' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5055','It is created in partnership with Greg Norman, the golf legend, also famously known as "The Shark." Designed to reflect his rare natural talent and relentless drive for perfection, this limited edition bottle is beautifully crafted in an exquisite decanter.
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','56','Xellent Swiss Vodka' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5056','Xellent vodka is pure, first-class Swiss Picasso and Matador rye grown in the alpine foothills of central Switzerland. The water comes from the Titlis glacier in Engelberg at the heart of central Swiss.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','57','Il Borro 2007' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5057','Il Borro is a Super Tuscan, produced by the renowned Salvatore Ferragamo Family of Italy with ambition. This wine is unique in that it is a mix of the Bordeaux and Syrah and thus boasts concentration, well beyond a regular Toscana.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','58','Grey Goose Vodka' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5058','Produced only with the finest French wheat and natural water filtered in limestone, Grey Goose Vodka contains incomparable freshness, smoothness, and clarity having gone through distillation process in the area of Cognac five times.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','59','A De Fussigny X.O.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5059','Building their own distillery by the Charente river bank in 1814, and with a storage to perfect the measure of humidity, a finest cognac has been produced with the skills of a master.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','60','62 Gun Salute' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5060','An extraordinarily rare blend of the most special whiskies set aside by each of the four Royal Salute Master Blenders since the brand’s creation in 1953, and stored for decades in the Royal Salute vault.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','61','Reignac 2005' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5061','Out of all Bordeaux wines, this wine is praised for its quality compared to its price. This wine won its popularity when it was introduced in ‘Les Gouttes de Dieu’ by Tadashi Agi, as an excellent wine for its price.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','62','Dior Addict Gloss' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5062','Ultra volume plus ultra shine equals visibly lusher lips. The spirit of Dior runway shows is captured in a collection of on-trend shades with made-to-measure effects.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','63','Estee Lauder Perfectionist' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','5063','Advanced with our revolutionary Wrinkle Lift Restructuring Peptides for more collagen. Wrinkles appear significantly reduced instantly and all day long.' );
INSERT INTO `labels` VALUES ('1','64','Lancome Melanolyser' );
